WEBVTT

00:00.145 --> 00:01.605
Previously on The O.C...

00:01.678 --> 00:05.129
I figured I'd do all right in a few surf competitions, maybe hook up with some sponsors.

00:05.208 --> 00:06.477
Turn that into a career, you know?

00:06.609 --> 00:08.847
I'll get the operation and get back on my board.

00:08.934 --> 00:09.733
What's going on with you guys?

00:09.818 --> 00:10.837
I can talk to him.

00:10.875 --> 00:13.676
Knowing that you're pulling for me is the only thing that keeps me going.

00:15.263 --> 00:16.117
Mom, hi.

00:16.203 --> 00:17.118
Hurry, I'm running late.

00:17.196 --> 00:19.259
If you'd just loosen up a little bit, you would be...

00:19.271 --> 00:20.807
I would be one of the popular girls.

00:20.884 --> 00:23.604
Truth is, I'm looking down the barrel of divorce number two.

00:23.690 --> 00:24.896
I live in a trailer park.

00:24.972 --> 00:27.744
No student has ever been involved in a shooting.

00:27.818 --> 00:29.674
Apparently, the parents are protesting.

00:29.837 --> 00:31.245
They want Marissa out.

00:33.000 --> 00:39.074
